                </TimeStamp> 
                                
                <description>
                     - Pamir Lodge. This is the place where you meet other overlanders and travellers. The garden is a pleasant spot overlooked by a wide open balcony where travellers enjoy their cooking or exhanging experiances. The lodge was established to fund the local jamoat khana. 
Price: 2 x 6,-U$/night/person
Campground: clean, quiet, we did sleep in our car 
Sanitair: OK, shower with warm water and toilet
Electricity: available
Wifi: yes (free)

